lwonder.world\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSocial Media: \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/smallwonder.world/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eInstagram\u003c/a\u003e / \u003ca href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@smallwonder.world\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTikTok\u003c/a\u003e / \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/smallwonder.world/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eFacebook\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat:\u003c/strong\u003e A Leaping Bunny Certified \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/hair-care\"\u003ehair-care\u003c/a\u003e brand that uses powerful, effective ingredients without the diluted fillers. Instead of single-use bottles filled with heavy water, Small Wonder offers a refillable and recyclable approach to \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/hair-care\"\u003ehair care\u003c/a\u003e that \u0026#34;transforms your shower routine into an experience of \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/luxury\"\u003eluxury\u003c/a\u003e.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrice Range:\u003c/strong\u003e $30-$38\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFounder:\u003c/strong\u003e Stephanie Farsht\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrigin Story:\u003c/strong\u003e Small Wonder is an innovative, professional-grade hair-care brand dedicated to revolutionizing the beauty industry with its powder-to-lather formulations. Known for its \u0026#34;salon-grade\u0026#34; powder products, Small Wonder elevates hair care by focusing on concentrated active ingredients, eliminating the need for unnecessary fillers or excess water. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAt the heart of the brand is its Wonder Bottle — a permanent, refillable fixture designed to reduce plastic waste while delivering luxurious, high-performance results. Paired with recyclable and compostable refill tubes, the packaging provides a more \u0026#34;sustainable\u0026#34; and efficient alternative to traditional hair-care products. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe brand has been recognized with several awards, including the Cosmoprof North America 2024 Award for its Signature Shampoo, the IDEA Award for its patented Wonder Bottle and the \u003cem\u003eMarie Claire \u003c/em\u003eAward for Best Refillable Packaging. With more than 60 years of industry expertise behind its creation, Small Wonder is redefining beauty by merging clean ingredients with uncompromising quality.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHero Products:\u003c/strong\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://fave.co/4hmPIVK\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSignature Shampoo\u003c/a\u003e ($38) and \u003ca href=\"https://fave.co/40JmCKM\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSignature Conditioner\u003c/a\u003e ($38)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePR Representation:\u003c/strong\u003e ExitOne Solutions\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to get in touch:\u003c/strong\u003e \u003ca href=\"mailto:%20hello@smallwonder.world\"\u003ehello@smallwonder.world\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eWant your brand featured? Hit the link below.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/page/brand-form\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-trac